{"tid":1891962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国徵召7艘客輪安置武漢醫護","createTime":"2020-02-22T08:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T10:06:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf99708b029acc9b2ad4201b8741361252108a5","tid":1891962,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"鑽石公主號的隔離方式導致船上3700餘人有634例確診，檢測為陰性搭乘撤僑包機回到家鄉的旅客陸續又被驗出陽性，如今中國竟徵召7艘長江三峽客輪，安置馳援武漢的各地醫護。<br />\n<br />\n據《新華社》報導，往返於中國宜昌和重慶的藍鯨號客輪，昨（21日）停靠於中國武漢漢口王家巷碼頭，為外地的醫療團隊提供住宿。除了藍鯨號之外，另有6艘客輪持續向武漢航行，這6艘船的床位加起來共有1267床。<br />\n<br />\n有客輪船長透露，船上配有防護服、口罩和專業消毒設備，每個房間的空調都是獨立的，就連空氣循環系統都有消毒裝置，因此可以保證醫護人員安全無虞。<br />\n<br />\n藍鯨號母公司中國長江航運集團表示，公司接到武漢市政府徵用的通知後，便從重慶、武漢挑選身體健康的船員，宜昌方面的人員則在第一時間做好船舶衛生與設備檢查。<br />\n<br />\n藍鯨號於1995年由武漢青山船廠建造，目前船上有101個標準客艙可供住宿，每個客艙裡有兩張床鋪，假如嚴格規定醫護人員1人1間的話，可以住進101人。<br />\n<br />\n在藍鯨號之外，還有宜昌江騰客船公司的仙娜、皇家花苑、皇家盛世、皇家星光，以及宜昌隆基旅運公司的長江孚泰、長江孚泰2號等6艘客輪正在前往武漢。<br />\n<br />\n中國當局之所以徵召以上7艘客輪，主因是武漢當地的飯店容量已接近飽和，徵召客輪讓外地援助武漢的醫療人員入住。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/22/phpvoCFhY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F22%2FphpvoCFhY.jpg&h=27db937b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（路透）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3076495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3076495&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AALe6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=0c439630\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3076495&h=2115b2c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3076495</a>"},{"pid":"d932bbbdc606e6b573e00ebb3c7dd971ef229ce4","tid":1891962,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:21:51.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"95d9383ea27992cd4b3922531b5c5aef93d0c34b","tid":1891962,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:21:57.000Z","msg":"［奶共美國公司］IG(facebook)奶共維穩證據<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1891917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1891917</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff7728dc1b009de95b486fc6d035e0f5ae8f0461","tid":1891962,"uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"變幽靈船？"},{"pid":"abac85569df5f694fecb2a1671174917e099528f","tid":1891962,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"又話受控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cea4498173f43446c41738e6a7428dbfcbadae","tid":1891962,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:36:02.000Z","msg":"7架鑽石公主號<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0d6a20d346b8c68db2efc63c1d4c1d18a07ac6","tid":1891962,"uid":173425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"呢7隻船死亡率實高過入火神雷神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86de3ec96d97faddd8e209d80b147a0b077d7aae","tid":1891962,"uid":336922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"直接dump落河<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n火都慳番<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3342895f088cef24434d1a30375520a6516a642","tid":1891962,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:57:39.000Z","msg":"鑽石公主號咪示範左<br />\n又想大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90573da08bcc3594656ececc812e42c31f3b00d7","tid":1891962,"uid":348984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"喺咪嫌日本唔夠柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.